Class CircleNode

java.lang.Object
  presentation.fsa.GraphElement

All Implemented Interfaces:
PresentationElement
public class CircleNode
extends Node

The circular representation of a state in a finite state automaton. Maintains a label and set of adjacent edges. Provides popup menu for operations

Author:
Helen Bretzke
See Also:
NodePopup.showPopup(presentation.fsa.GraphDrawingView, presentation.fsa.CircleNode)
